headline: LKQ Corporation to Present at Upcoming Investor Conference
summary: ANTIOCH, Tenn., Aug. 07, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- LKQ Corporation (Nasdaq: LKQ), today announced that members of its senior management will be presenting at the following investor conference: J.P. Morgan 2025 Automotive Conference August 12, 2025 New York, New York Materials used during the presentation will be posted to the Company's website: www.lkqcorp.com on the day of the conference.
